These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, time-travel, satire, family, mystery, action
 1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching family movies##7
 3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching scientific movies##7
 4. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 5. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 6. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person watching action movies##7
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific | horror | time-travel | satire | mystery | action |

