.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, baseball, tennis, cricket, volleyball, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Sport   | tennis | biathlon | volleyball | surfing | baseball | basketball | cricket |

