.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, camping, magic-tricks, skydiving, gardening, card-games
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | gardening | magic-tricks | card-games | board-games | camping | sudoku |

