.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, tea, mirinda, almond-milk, sprite, iced-tea
 1. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking mirinda##7
 6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 7. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Beverage   | tea | water | mirinda | iced-tea | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | sprite |

