 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##7
 8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking 7up##2
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |       3       |    4     |      5      |  6   |    7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | cola | tea | coffee | fanta | 7up | sprite |

