 6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
10. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
12. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
14. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
